products.title: Clear Transparent Pvc Covid-19 Roller Blind
products.description: This product is designed to protect both your customers and employees from the potential spread of covid-19. This fire retardent pvc transparent roller blind is perfect for use to segregate staff in retail environments, without losing light or visibility of your workplace. These blinds have been used above counter tops, between factory workers and too between retail workers (such as hairdressers and nail parlours).
